Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…會死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:51.54,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\pos(210,550)}愛將征服一切。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.03,0:01:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夜之愛子是能無限產生魔力的寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:01:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但身體非常虛弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}活著就會不斷重複吸收和產生魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.67,0:02:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最後身體會不堪重負
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你很清楚啊 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他放著身處危險的你不管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了滿足他的好奇 放任地讓你活著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那時的頭暈…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.97,0:02:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 他沒有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他只是裝成人類的冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別指望他會像人一樣愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是他買下的 這是你無形的枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他還對你施了追蹤術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.55,0:02:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們會幫你恢復自由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}師父
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡是我們的地盤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}魔術師不許在這裡惹事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你還好嗎 艾瑞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 離開鐵絲就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼 你不想要解脫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從哪裡解脫？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.37,0:03:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果你是指艾利亞斯 你恐怕不了解他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪怕只是謊言 只有艾利亞斯稱我為家人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說的是真是假都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他比任何人還快就將我買下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以直到艾利亞斯放開我 我都是他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是影子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}潛藏在荊棘之影下的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們稱我為裂噬之城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還好吧 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓我看看傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}傷口？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真亂來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類受了傷 很快就會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來得太慢了 身為影子還這麼沒存在感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有智世在 我也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}束縛快要解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.83,0:04:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 這裡沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻煩你把這淨化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也同行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}國王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用擔心啦 是我和智世一起淨化呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果這片汙穢能消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身為國王 最後的責任就是見證這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 智世 你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很久以前的小酒店 吃東西的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:10.02,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鄰鎮可漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:12.41,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽說有好多美女啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}透明的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這裡好像是那片汙穢的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:26.97,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就是漂泊的魔術師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看到是個小孩 有嚇到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什麼要商量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}旅行久了 總會有人找我幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}農作物歉收嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是想奪得女孩的歡心？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是 我太太天生身體虛弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總是臥病在床 我想讓她重獲健康
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您有沒有什麼好藥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您真喜歡夫人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想都不想嗎 你挺羞澀的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以讓我見見夫人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻煩您了 請立刻來一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他不是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你 好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我和您丈夫談一談
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請問 情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}提姆 提姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了 提姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恐怕不會再有所好轉 只能活幾年了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是天生的 沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜從小就不能出門玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明本性勤奮 卻因為體弱不得不臥床
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她真的很可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要是我能做到的事 我都願意去做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}求你了 我真的不忍心看她這樣死去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您夫人喜歡貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.98,0:08:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎 那倒是有一個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你知道嗎 貓有九條命哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又是老鼠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最近老鼠是不是變多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}家貓們不會都在偷懶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜 你出來走動不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 今天天氣也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欸 你們看到馬修嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我剛才去送午餐 但他不在田裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說不定是去和哪個女人幽會了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:37.94,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全村的人都知道馬修對米娜一心一意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我剛才看到他拿著斧頭進了森林
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:39.94,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我開玩笑的啦 開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}森林？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修 馬修？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你臉色好差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有一種很不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}房子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原來這裡還有間房子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修真是的 在這裡做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可以看裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你今天身體狀態不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正好 我剛剛製作完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是給你的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修 你在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前不是讓魔術師看過病嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:12:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他說只要做出這種靈藥給你服用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就能治好你的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}貓呢 這些貓是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都是材料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.21,0:12:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人們說貓有九條命 其實那是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以把貓的生命收集起來 就能做成靈藥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種畜生居然有那麼多條命 真不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修 欸 馬修你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.31,0:12:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼要做這麼殘忍的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不是會做出這種事的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我做得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為都是為了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身體動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的 不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喝下那個 你就能從不自由的身體中解放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:13:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不僅如此 還有可能獲得永久的壽命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你…對馬修做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是稍微取得信用而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒事的 這可是很棒的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來當我的小白鼠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜 不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只有一開始會痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍耐一下 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣就能獲得健康的身體了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是幸運的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}失敗了嗎 身體崩壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}畜生終究只是畜生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算比人類容易加工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但本能很強 所以反噬的詛咒也更強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來要先重新研究如何凝縮靈魂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你提供了寶貴的實驗結果 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜 米娜 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼米娜會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.47,0:14:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎呀 壞掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}愛真是偉大啊 大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:15:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼 為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還需要…更多更多更多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}必須收集更多才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要去收集 更多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}提姆 你來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你最喜歡的米娜現在很不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:16:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你已經不再是人 變成惡魔了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成了被惡魔欺騙的可憐惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不能讓你活下去 也不能讓你安穩地死去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為我是牠們選出的王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是為了那些死去的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不在 我好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓你看到不好的回憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.09,0:17:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本來只想請你消除掉我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但你有很強的觀察力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「消除」是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是字面意思 讓我們消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}生物的靈魂終將回歸輪迴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我和馬修都忘記了如何回歸輪迴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那些貓也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遭到殺害 許下詛咒的貓的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都忘記了該如何回歸輪迴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以希望你能消除掉我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.35,0:17:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們只是被欺騙了 不應該這樣消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}錯過這次 前方會有更無盡痛苦的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.04,0:18:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以現在只有你能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就由我來做指引吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}國王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這已是我的第九條命 不久將回歸塵土
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的話 應該能指引你們前進的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 絕對不行 那孩子會傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}死亡總是突然又平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}或早或晚 終將來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛才的王 還有之前的王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了抑制汙穢 都獻上了自己的靈魂為祭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼一想 指引一程就相對輕鬆多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我擁有和那孩子的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾瑞爾 你的話…用你的力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你能將花種送往千里之外的風…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}花種入土 落花為肥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}便是土地和風的盟約
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該回歸輪迴的事物 就該回歸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類真是 又傻又聰明又有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我們無法離開你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.18,0:19:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會讓你消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別擔心 她會帶你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以你也想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蒲公英的種子乘風而行的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想像自己在那裡生根發芽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想像風兒帶著你前往應至的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:26.73,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}目の前のその青に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:33.63,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}届かない事を知る
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:39.99,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}同じ空見てたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:45.54,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}君は遠い雲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:53.44,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}夕暮れに月を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:21:00.34,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}行き先も知らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:06.24,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}いつかは覚める夢も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:12.54,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}思い出せるように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:24.23,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}空に流れ着いた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:30.71,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}手をつなぐ様に舞う花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:37.54,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}微かに聞こえている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:45.35,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}通じ合える言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:26.73,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}眼前的那片蔚藍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:33.63,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}我知道自己捉摸不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:39.99,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}明明望著同一片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:45.54,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}你卻是天邊那朵孤雲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:53.44,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}傍晚時分 我追尋著月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:21:00.34,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}漫無目標地四處奔走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:06.24,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}只希望回想起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:12.54,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}那終將甦醒的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:24.23,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}隨風飄蕩 飛向天際
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:30.71,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}曼舞的花瓣 好像你我緊牽的手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:37.54,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}我聽見那輕輕的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:45.35,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5}是我們呢喃的愛語
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:20:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}米娜 你都跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬修 走吧馬修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}親愛的小魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望你還不會來我們這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:21:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我原本是個沒人要的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無人想收留我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.12,0:22:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一次又一次被拋棄 掙扎為生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終於找到了一個可能的巢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我什麼時候會死呢
Comment: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.49,0:22:44.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}枝に結ぶ　実が熟す前に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:49.36,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}落ちてしまわぬよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.28,0:22:57.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}苦しいほどに　また咲き乱れる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.59,0:23:02.57,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}朝へ　つなぐよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:14.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}何度繰り返し　繰り返し　生まれても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.38,0:23:28.02,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}いつも　新しい　空を見せてあげよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:39.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}誰もまだ誰も　書いてない物語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.37,0:23:54.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}白い　真っ白い地図に　描いてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.49,0:22:44.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}別不待結上枝頭 果實成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:49.36,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}便早早飄落在地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.28,0:22:57.45,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}越是風吹雨打 越要爛漫綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.59,0:23:02.57,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}迎向嶄新的朝霞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:14.58,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}一遍遍 又是一遍遍 你誕生在世
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.38,0:23:28.02,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}我依舊 會為你帶來 又一片藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:39.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}是誰 又是誰 寫下嶄新的篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.37,0:23:54.19,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}鋪開 純白的地圖 描繪軌跡 歌唱明天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.10,0:24:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}指引靈魂的代價很大
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.74,0:24:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}墜入沉睡的少女和守護她的魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.99,0:24:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}出現在兩人面前的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能介紹你的妻子給我嗎

